														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3814331">
									

<p>So just that I'm clear on what's going on here: this device (in addition to its primary function of memory retrieval) is actually harvesting parts of peoples brains, which they no longer remember exist because of the Lethe events, and using that brain tissue to generate mnestic drugs, among other things, like putting them together in a giant uber-brain?</p>
<p>I'm not clear if everyone forgetting the device at the end is intentional on Bruce's part or not, since in his last note he doesn't express any desire to keep this a secret.</p>

