			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3819720">
									

<p>The continual omission of this device by marketing department seems like initially 3848 for this device have initially hit the marketing department and then later spread on to affect MC&amp;D and maybe even the foundation after they took these as the device is not mentioned in 3848 containment procedure.</p>
<p>Edit: After reading the paperpushing tale it seems like the foundation is currently making use of this device so the foundation is not affected. And then from that tale it have been shown that the foundation have become under public knowledge since 1990 while this tale also mentioned the foundation despite not mentioning SCP foundation. I don't think the foundation is affected in this case.</p>

